title: AUTODESK.SIMULATION.MOLDFLOW.INSIGHT.ULTIMATE.V2016.MULTI.WIN64-
description:
Simulation tools for injection molding
Autodesk Simulation Moldflow provides simulation tools for injection 
mold design, plastic part design, and the injection molding design process. 
The software guides you through setup and results to show how changes 
to gate location, material, and geometry affect manufacturability 
for thermoset and thermoplastic materials.
